name: The Queen's Dreams: Spin City
description:
The cars hummed and whirred barely audible over the neon lights and buzzing billboards. Everyone was just so busy.
Captions, slogans, slang, all crass but entrapping at the same time.
The City pulled you in. 
The fame.
The opportunity.
She could a achieve anything in this playground and she was good at it.
She played the game and it played back. The City was alive. The City was fun.
